      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 61,
      "message": "Yes. This is ok to be null. In most of the cases ToscaServiceTemplateFragment will be null, In some cases like specified in https://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/The+CLAMP+Policy+Framework+Participant, There could be some new policy-types or policies that need to be deployed to Policy-Framework. These policies may not already exist in Policy DB. This fragment of ToscaServiceTemplate is used in such cases.",
